{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n  <body>\n    <h2>最新天文台天氣報告｜未來五天香港天氣預報</h2>\n    <p>天文台展望，明日氣溫回升，有一兩陣驟雨。星期日驟雨逐漸增多及有狂風雷暴。隨後一兩日大致多雲，早上稍涼。</p>\n    <table>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>日期</cell>\n        <cell>5月1日(五)</cell>\n        <cell>5月2日(六)</cell>\n        <cell>5月3日(日)</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>最高溫度</cell>\n        <cell>26度</cell>\n        <cell>28度</cell>\n        <cell>29度</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>最低溫度</cell>\n        <cell>22度</cell>\n        <cell>24度</cell>\n        <cell>23度</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>風向及級數</cell>\n        <cell>東至東北風4級，離岸間中5級。</cell>\n        <cell>東南風3至4級。</cell>\n        <cell>南風3級，晚上北風4級。</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>濕度</cell>\n        <cell>70-90%</cell>\n        <cell>70-90%</cell>\n        <cell>70-95%</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>顯著降雨概率</cell>\n        <cell>低</cell>\n        <cell>低</cell>\n        <cell>中高</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>天氣</cell>\n        <cell>大致多雲。早晚有一兩陣雨，日間部分時間天色明朗。</cell>\n        <cell>大致多雲，有一兩陣驟雨。下午短暫時間有陽光。</cell>\n        <cell>大致多雲，有幾陣驟雨。初時短暫時間有陽光。稍後驟雨增多，局部地區有狂風雷暴。</cell>\n      </row>\n    </table>\n    <table>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>日期</cell>\n        <cell>5月4日(一)</cell>\n        <cell>5月5日(二)</cell>\n        <cell>5月6日(三)</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>最高溫度</cell>\n        <cell>27度</cell>\n        <cell>26度</cell>\n        <cell>27度</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>最低溫度</cell>\n        <cell>22度</cell>\n        <cell>22度</cell>\n        <cell>23度</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>風向及級數</cell>\n        <cell>北至東北風4級。</cell>\n        <cell>東風4級，間中5級。</cell>\n        <cell>東風4級，間中5級。</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>濕度</cell>\n        <cell>65-90%</cell>\n        <cell>70-90%</cell>\n        <cell>70-90%</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>顯著降雨概率</cell>\n        <cell>低</cell>\n        <cell>低</cell>\n        <cell>低</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>天氣</cell>\n        <cell>大致多雲。早晚有一兩陣驟雨。</cell>\n        <cell>大致多雲。日間部分時間天色明朗。</cell>\n        <cell>短暫時間有陽光。</cell>\n      </row>\n    </table>\n  </body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-30T23:18:00.705807+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":484,"images":0,"source":"GoTrip","fallback":"none"}}